      "writtenOn": "2017-12-04T21:07:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This one is more necessary. Subsequent invocations of GN will remember this because the arguments are saved in build.ninja. If it\u0027s not abspath()d, then gn writes it as literally \"--runtime-deps-list-file\u003dout/fuch/targets.txt\", which won\u0027t exist on regeneration because regeneration is run from a cwd of out/fuch. Alternatively, we could chdir out/fuch before running this, or pursue it as a GN bug (it seems to abspath the --root argument internally). But abspath() seemed easiest.",
      "parentUuid": "1e014bc7_a9336f25",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 41,
        "startChar": 17,
        "endLine": 41,
        "endChar": 32
